metadata.name: Last Inhale and Exhale.
metadata.description:
This is a audio and video sequence Last Inhale and Exhale from music clip Inhale Exhale by JAF 34.
.
Inhale Exhale tells of the last phase of life, when old people are lonely, often no joy or rejoicing in a new day, just pills, memories of the past, waiting for the end, and the last inhale and exhale. 
.
1/1, Size: 1920x1080px
